response.original_title: Wilco - Live at the Civic Theater - First Night
response.overview: The band played a 25-song set that night, including songs from the new album (Cruel Country) and older favorites.  The setlist included: "Misunderstood" "Cruel Country" "I Am Trying to Break Your Heart" "Jesus, Etc." "California Stars" (a Billy Bragg & Wilco song) "Heavy Metal Drummer" "Spiders (Kidsmoke)" "Red-Eyed and Blue" "I Got You (At the End of the Century)" "U.S. Blues" (Grateful Dead cover)
response.title: Wilco - Live at the Civic Theater - First Night
